.. code:: console

   $ exp509 --help
   usage: exp509 [-h] -t N HOST[:PORT] [HOST[:PORT] ...]

   positional arguments:
     HOST[:PORT]

   options:
     -h, --help           show this help message and exit
     -t N, --threshold N  alert when cert expires in N days (or less)

   $ exp509 -t 90 jwilk.net
   jwilk.net: certificate expires on 2017-11-20 03:04

